    <item>
      <title>美联储发言人称市场为大数据周做准备，美国国债价格下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/treasuries-drop-as-market-braces-for-big-data-week-fed-speakers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员等待本周的大量经济数据和美联储官员讲话，美国国债周一缩减早盘跌幅，这些讲话可能会决定本月晚些时候央行政策决定的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/treasuries-drop-as-market-braces-for-big-data-week-fed-speakers</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 14:27:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚重返欧洲债券市场，发行 22 亿美元债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/nigeria-s-latest-eurobond-sale-should-see-solid-demand-says-rmb</link>
      <description><![CDATA[分析师表示，尼日利亚两年多来首次发行欧洲债券，吸引了强劲的投资者需求，这使得政府能够收紧 22 亿美元债券的定价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/nigeria-s-latest-eurobond-sale-should-see-solid-demand-says-rmb</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 11:34:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>勒庞支持不信任投票，法国资产承压</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/french-bonds-fall-as-le-pen-piles-pressure-on-barnier-again</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在玛丽娜·勒庞领导的政党表示将支持对法国总理米歇尔·巴尼耶政府进行不信任投票后，法国债券和股票再度面临抛售压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/french-bonds-fall-as-le-pen-piles-pressure-on-barnier-again</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 08:10:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
